      "updated": 1782380000000,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Provider Layer\n\nEntry: getProviderPriority / chooseScoreSource lines 2657-2755\nResolver: resolveProviderMatch lines 2451-2512\n\nEffective ladders:\n- Live tennis: SofaScore live board -> ESPN tennis date board\n- Cricket: ESPNcricinfo -> LiveScore\n- Mapped soccer: ESPN -> SofaScore -> API-Football\n- Unmapped soccer: SofaScore -> API-Football\n- Rugby/AFL: ESPN/SofaScore -> API-Sports/LiveScore\n- Esports: PandaScore when enabled and token-configured\n\nParser homes: _findEspn, _findEspnTennis, _findSofascore, _findApiFootball, _findApiSports, _findPandaScore",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Provider Layer\n\nEntry: getProviderPriority / chooseScoreSource lines 2657-2755\nResolver: resolveProviderMatch lines 2451-2512\n\nEffective ladders:\n- Live tennis: SofaScore live board -> ESPN tennis date board\n- Cricket: ESPNcricinfo -> LiveScore\n- Mapped soccer: ESPN -> SofaScore -> API-Football\n- Unmapped soccer: SofaScore -> API-Football\n- Rugby/AFL: ESPN/SofaScore -> API-Sports/LiveScore\n- Esports: PandaScore when enabled and token-configured\n\nParser homes: _findEspn, _findEspnTennis, _findSofascore, _findApiFootball, _findApiSports, _findPandaScore",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
