      "text": "Test Harness\n\ntests/load-userscript.js loads the real userscript into a Node vm and exposes selected internals.\nImportant suites: providers.test.js, sofascore.test.js, matching.test.js, cache.test.js, byok-quota.test.js, render-states.test.js, security.test.js.\nRun from tests: npm.cmd test",
