      "originalText": "Where To Start\n\nProvider failed: docs/PROVIDER_NOTES.md -> provider parser -> provider tests.\nWrong match: matching core -> candidate diagnostics -> matching.test.js.\nPanel layout bug: renderers/CSS -> render-states.test.js and manual Torn smoke test.\nQuota/API key issue: BYOK ledger -> api-sports/pandascore/odds settings rows.\nRelease/debug report issue: metadata, buildDebugReport, CHANGELOG.md.",
